      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a well-cared-for 2019 Lexus ES 350 in Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle has been consistently garaged and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep luster, showing only minor road-wear such as small stone chips on the lower front valance and a tiny, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the Parchment interior remains crisp and smoke-free; the leather seating is supple, with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every electronic component, from the heated/ventilated seats to the premium infotainment system, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 runs quietly and delivers smooth power through the 8-speed transmission. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive multi-point inspection, a fresh synthetic oil change, and a brake fluid flush. The tires are matching Michelins with significant tread life remaining. This car represents a perfect balance of luxury and reliability, showing the pride of previous ownership in every detail. Complete service records are available upon request.",
